  "body": "### Description\n_Type_: Bug\n_Summary_: introduced in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/7919 - decision was to fix it separately. \"Fetch messages\" still can lead to the endless spinner when the app goes offline-online during fetching. \n\n#### Expected behavior\nmessages fetched normally\n\n#### Actual behavior\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/55971883-9f528500-5c82-11e9-9bd6-b3e399175304.png\n\n### Reproduction\n**Prerequisites:** \"Fetch messages\" should be shown (app offline for > 24h)\n\n* Open chat with \"Fetch messages\"\n* tap on it\n* go to offline \n* go back online\n\n### Additional Information\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\n\n* Status version: nightly 13/04/2019\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\n\n",
